{"tid":2069455,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"暴徒學校李賢堯紀念中學居然有學生影班相做五一手勢","createTime":"2020-06-18T11:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T11:49:28.000Z","uid":260817,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1fe39820df33277b378abef87368120b8d5c801e","tid":2069455,"uid":260817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUJrPfR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUJrPfR.png&h=1bbb3d05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NjCbue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NjCbue.png&h=3adf0c8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t14Oh9h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft14Oh9h.png&h=103cdd63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教育界近日濔漫白色恐怖，中學畢業生就連在畢業照中做手勢支持「五大訴求」竟也被打壓。《蘋果》收到一群來自中華傳道會李賢堯紀念中學的畢業生投訴，指控有攝影師擅自修改畢業大合照，打壓學生言論自由。因不少學生拍畢業照時舉起寓意「五大訴求，缺一不可」的「五一」手勢，但攝影師曬相後竟「P圖」，至少把5名學生的「五一」手勢竄改成「四二」手勢，令五大訴求「消失」。有家長後來幾番追究攝影師及取回原圖，卻不得要領，對方更辯稱改圖「是學校的指示」，家長不禁批評學界失自由，「連一個手勢都容納唔到！」"},{"pid":"8f0b7e95806a06b4f6ece75922dcc0535d9dfa78","tid":2069455,"uid":260817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:40:00.000Z","msg":"推到俾啲黃屍見到"},{"pid":"f3e5fa09d9d65c2deb937bb5a7b3c457fd65e173","tid":2069455,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"柒到無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c66dfe7fb642afdf55c1b3aad18f2d1d4938c41","tid":2069455,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:49:28.000Z","msg":"又哂一個account"}]}